media:group.media:title: User Interface: The Toolbar
media:group.media:description:
In this video we're taking the first but a very good look at Ardour's user interface.
The Toolbar contains crucial controls for working with your session, so in this video I'll explain and demonstrate every part of it.

Learn more in the Ardour Manual:
http://manual.ardour.org/ardours-interface/about/

Get Ardour:
http://ardour.org
